OL,3,CBorders Bowling Club loses its home as
OL,4,Ccouncil plans for gymnastics centre
OL,6,FMembers of Tweedbank Indoor Bowling
OL,7,FClub say they are devastated by the
OL,8,Fdecision to turn the building they've
OL,9,Fused for more than 40 years, into a
OL,10,Fgymnastics and soft play centre.
OL,12,FWe filmed with them ahead of the
OL,13,Fdecision to hear their thoughts and
OL,14,Fconcerns.
OL,16,FThey've now launched a petition to
OL,17,Fsave what they have called a 'vital
OL,18,Fcommunity facility."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
