OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779711071
OL,3,CBorders Bowling Club loses its home as
OL,4,Ccouncil plans for gymnastics centre
OL,6,F"Tweedbank Indoor Bowling Club is not
OL,7,Fjust a sports venue, it is a lifeline
OL,8,Ffor many people across the Central
OL,9,FBorders," says President Malcolm Thin.
OL,11,F"It provides a safe, welcoming
OL,12,Fenvironment where individuals of all
OL,13,Fages, particularly our senior members
OL,14,Fcan stay active, socialise, and
OL,15,Fmaintain their mental wellbeing. Its
OL,16,Floss would leave a significant gap in
OL,17,Fcommunity provision and increase the
OL,18,Frisk of isolation for many.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
