PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779711071
OL,3,CBorders Bowling Club loses its home as
OL,4,Ccouncil plans for gymnastics centre
OL,6,F"This decision would end indoor
OL,7,Fbowling in the Central Borders. For a
OL,8,Fregion with a strong bowling
OL,9,Ftradition, this would be a devastating
OL,10,Fblow."
OL,12,FThe property is operated by Live
OL,13,FBorders which is making a number of
OL,14,Fchanges to the services it delivers in
OL,15,Forder to maximise usage and income,
OL,16,Ffollowing years of financial
OL,17,Fdifficulties.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
