OL,3,CBorders Bowling Club loses its home as
OL,4,Ccouncil plans for gymnastics centre
OL,6,FAt a full meeting of Scottish Borders
OL,7,FCouncil on Thursday 21 May,
OL,8,Fcouncillors accepted recommendations
OL,9,Fto spend half a million pounds
OL,10,Ftransforming the building into a
OL,11,Fgymnastics and soft play centre.
OL,13,FPlans which are predicted to bring in
OL,14,F#150,000 of income annually by 2031/32.
OL,16,FThe council report states: "The
OL,17,Fdevelopment of the bowling hall into a
OL,18,Ffamily-oriented centre would help
OL,19,Frejuvenate the wider site.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779711071
OL,3,CBorders Bowling Club loses its home as
OL,4,Ccouncil plans for gymnastics centre
OL,6,F"An extensive adventure play facility
OL,7,Fcould be built alongside gymnastics
OL,8,Fwithin the bowling hall, which is too
OL,9,Flarge for gymnastics alone. Dance and
OL,10,Fteen fitness can also take place on
OL,11,Fadditional floor space and in the
OL,12,Fstudio area. Children's parties will
OL,13,Fbe a significant source of income."
OL,15,FIt says this would generate
OL,16,F"significantly more footfall and
OL,17,Fimpact than indoor bowling, which is
OL,18,Fonly played for five months of the
OL,19,Fyear, and membership has reduced to
OL,20,Funder 100."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
