CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779711071
OL,3,CBorders Bowling Club loses its home as
OL,4,Ccouncil plans for gymnastics centre
OL,6,FIt added that work could start as
OL,7,Fearly as January 2027.
OL,9,FIn November 2025, Scottish Borders
OL,10,FCouncil agreed to a range of measures
OL,11,Fdesigned to deliver combined annual
OL,12,Fsavings and increased income of #2.2m
OL,13,Ffor the charitable body Live Borders,
OL,14,Fwho runs sporting, cultural, and
OL,15,Fleisure facilities on its behalf.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
