FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779711071
OL,3,CBorders Bowling Club loses its home as
OL,4,Ccouncil plans for gymnastics centre
OL,6,FThis followed an independent report
OL,7,Fpublished in April 2025, which
OL,8,Frecommended the closure of a number of
OL,9,Fbuildings in order to save the
OL,10,Forganisation money and help sustain
OL,11,Fits future.
OL,13,FThe bowling club is now asking Live
OL,14,FBorders and Scottish Borders Council
OL,15,Fto 'work with them' to find a solution
OL,16,Fthat allows bowling to continue
OL,17,Falongside any future developments.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/8
